    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with the original factory paint preserved under a professional ceramic coating; there are no chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury, featuring pristine leather upholstery that still carries that new-car scent, untouched carpets, and a dashboard free of any sun wear or scratches. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a full paper trail included. With exceptionally low mileage and a smooth, responsive powertrain, it offers a driving experience that is tight, quiet, and powerful. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously pampered example for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
